msgid ""
"<strong>Warning:</strong> To capture the amount manually, you also need to "
"set\n"
"                    the Capture Delay to manual on your Adyen account "
"settings."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Advarsel:</strong> For at indtaste beløbet manuelt skal du også "
"indstille\n"
"                    indtastningsforsinkelsen til ‘manuelt’ i indstillingerne "
"på din Adyen-konto."

